{"tid":538710,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日覺得自己發燒但其實體溫偏低","createTime":"2018-01-24T01:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T02:54:51.000Z","uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d1e5c8e957b1e130d7be19413b6d744cc25b85","tid":538710,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T01:03:34.000Z","msg":"發燒食退燒藥就聽得多<br />\n但係經常個人熱辣辣又頭痛<br />\n但係度出黎體溫偏低又應該點處理？<br />\n有時身邊人掂我都覺得我好似發燒咁熱<br />\n但係走去量體溫一直keep住得36度左右<br />\n依兩日得35.5<br />\n係保暖出問題？但係我唔覺得好凍<br />\n我情緒好唔穩定 關唔關事？<br />\n<br />\n唔好屌我唔睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我睇過 佢話叫我試下著重返保暖先再睇下點 又話我太緊張<br />\n但係我搵資料話35.5已經漸入低溫症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁即係點 我好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee61a6b16f3948cc5e3e41567be362773efbd0b","tid":538710,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T01:04:52.000Z","msg":"長期 唔止冬天"},{"pid":"90f38eab9d499704ff1ea56c7cbc248e6f0694de","tid":538710,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T01:43:05.000Z","msg":"保暖先"},{"pid":"73387444ba26fbdc72ea44f77fd9fbf3fff4e4ba","tid":538710,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T01:51:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89c02e2ed53a462cc0d6b1fe24b50be9984e7e4c","tid":538710,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90f38eab9d499704ff1ea56c7cbc248e6f0694de","tid":538710,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T01:43:05.000Z","msg":"保暖先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T02:19:40.000Z","msg":"嘗試中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8370966d52775d854548d5dc3fb47c9a5467d7e3","tid":538710,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73387444ba26fbdc72ea44f77fd9fbf3fff4e4ba","tid":538710,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T